---
// src/components/Footer.astro
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-[#020408] text-gray-400 pt-20 pb-10 border-t border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden font-['Montserrat']">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none" 
         style="background-image: url('https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/ec/World_map_blank_without_borders.svg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 relative z-10">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-16 border-b border-white/10 pb-12">
            <div class="md:col-span-5">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">SMA ABBS <span class="text-yellow-600">Surakarta</span></h2>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 mb-6 max-w-sm">
                    Mewujudkan generasi ulul albab yang berakhlak mulia, berprestasi tinggi dalam sains, dan berwawasan global.
                </p>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-yellow-600 hover:border-yellow-600 hover:text-white transition duration-300 rounded-sm"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-red-600 hover:border-red-600 hover:text-white transition duration-300 rounded-sm"><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col md:items-end justify-center">
                <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-light mb-2">Jangan Lewatkan Informasi PPDB</h3>
                <form class="flex w-full md:w-auto">
                    <input type="email" placeholder="Masukkan Email Anda" class="bg-white/5 border border-gray-700 text-white px-6 py-3 w-full md:w-80 focus:outline-none focus:border-yellow-600 transition text-sm rounded-l-sm placeholder-gray-600 rounded-none">
                    <button class="bg-yellow-600 text-black px-6 py-3 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-yellow-500 transition rounded-r-sm rounded-none">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i>
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center pt-8 border-t border-white/5 text-xs text-gray-600">
            <p>&copy; {currentYear} SMA ABBS Surakarta. High Performance School.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-6 mt-4 md:mt-0">
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Terms of Service</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>